Swipe Crime, not just a show but a journey, not just for me but for many. These ten pictures aren’t really enough to encapsulate my journey of working in this very special project but well I tried. 
Fun, enriching, wholesome are a few words I could use to describe this experience. As clichéd as this may sound, what started as mere professional associations truly did turn into friendships and beyond on this one, we turned into one big family! We have laughed, cried, fumed, consoled, hated and loved together, in these two years we have lived together. I am grateful to have gotten to be a part of Swipe Crime and the love that all of you have showered upon us and this show has been the biggest cherry on top! 
A big thank you to each and every person involved in the making of Swipe Crime for making it the show and journey that it has been. 
And of course a BIG thank you to all for watching it and giving it sooo much love!!🥰❤️
Only onwards and upwards from here!! 
Feel free to spam @mr_mainra to ask about season 2!🤭
